title: Beachbody CEO on `Communal' Fitness
itunes:title: Beachbody CEO on `Communal' Fitness
description:
Carl Daikeler, Co-Founder and CEO of Beachbody, discusses the business of in-home, on-demand fitness. He explains how social media has helped the growth of their digital subscription business.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
